entries.femaleVariant: What they did to you... that is not OK, no, not OK. You must do something.
Yeah, like what? I'm a nobody, an' nobody gives a lick about me.
Not true. Go to the Mox. Tell them what happened. They will help you, you'll see.
Pff, why? My tear jerker gonna move them?
We whores have our dignity, dammit. We should do everything to defend it.
